{"id": 876, "genre": 1001, "title": "一句话说明你是一个与世无争的人？", "description": "豆瓣电影常年打4分，遇到极难看的电影也打3分，谦谦君子，云淡风轻。", "record_count": 5041, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2016070218364902k47uNRTCSvf1Y8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-29T11:29:00Z", "options": [{"id": 62464, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530141}, {"id": 63744, "content": "都别给我点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547926}, {"id": 64000, "content": "什么是伐木累", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 318325}, {"id": 62465, "content": "你开心就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539187}, {"id": 62467, "content": "还行吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 483214}, {"id": 62723, "content": "关我屁事和关你屁事", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161905}, {"id": 63491, "content": "是我的，何必争", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546632}, {"id": 62469, "content": "加入了很多群，状态永远是“潜水”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531762}, {"id": 64005, "content": "热闹是你们的，我什么也没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 549133}, {"id": 62470, "content": "减肥是一直没有实现的事儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539195}, {"id": 62726, "content": "gfc", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498620}, {"id": 62471, "content": "我静静的看着你们就好～", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531274}, {"id": 62472, "content": "出来留言的都不是与世无争的～与世无争的都浏览无痕～", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531274}, {"id": 62473, "content": "不还价", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508569}, {"id": 62985, "content": "我刚来闹市", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541506}, {"id": 65289, "content": "在考场睡觉，拿着不及格的卷子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 550363}, {"id": 64522, "content": "❤️", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508918}, {"id": 62475, "content": "hhh", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539207}, {"id": 63243, "content": "挺好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 543928}, {"id": 62476, "content": "塞传单总是习惯性接着", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539206}, {"id": 62988, "content": "你好【微笑】", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541531}, {"id": 65036, "content": "苟全性命于乱世 不求闻达于诸侯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 556283}, {"id": 62477, "content": "好漂亮啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 410555}, {"id": 62478, "content": "呵呵哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532061}, {"id": 62990, "content": "缺钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541545}, {"id": 62479, "content": "我不需要你们给我点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 503507}, {"id": 66576, "content": "随便", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564116}, {"id": 58640, "content": "跟人聊天没什么废话，你说啥，我就说“好”", "image": null, "praise_count": 241, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 62480, "content": "算了\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 264165}, {"id": 58641, "content": "豆瓣打分常年4分", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 62993, "content": "我觉得不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533288}, {"id": 63249, "content": "切！", "im